{"tid":1143034,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［WhatsApp］影視綜藝吹水台","createTime":"2019-05-07T12:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T03:06:11.000Z","uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1fa620a712d48bbf36deb9d91e102612aba5b61b","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:44:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家平日都應該會睇開各類影視娛樂野，有電視有電視劇，當大家想搵人討論下劇情，又或者有啲好戲 or 另類戲 想搵腳睇但又未必搵到<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，呢個gp正正比大家一個渠道去討論劇情，推介下近期好睇既作品，又或者即興組團睇戲都得，入面咩劇都討論得，美劇、韓劇、日劇、港劇，電影的話咩類型都可以吹下水<br />\n<br />\n想入gp既，可以填資料，admin 會盡快add你～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScMeIyWfoCDXrzN-czOQpqMw7KPBg10NHqDLEpmZ84jotFuZw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScMeIyWfoCDXrzN-czOQpqMw7KPBg10NHqDLEpmZ84jotFuZw%2Fviewform&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8S25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=ec998709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScMeIyWfoCDXrzN-czOQpqMw7KPBg10NHqDLEpmZ84jotFuZw/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e813fcf9221d3347291ea630165f40d50fd822e4","tid":1143034,"uid":94465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"本身已經有個gp定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f672930cad9839c94d1d88448a7ec0ef5f437b28","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"個gp暫時有10個人左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ec4daae798ec9758dada3c5804c175a901cc5f","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:29:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e15904916ee82bb9e2c4439b07546599afd1e07","tid":1143034,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5月11日 星期六 早上8點半<br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></strong>"},{"pid":"dc33a4eb41ba2393a6133596d6abff7af33a5328","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75199c19f80eb3d7ffb5c0164d6c9e5d8a14bbfc","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a5190dc04bcdca15d44076fcb9d9b6e704f6cae","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:05:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dca4181e5007f7c344edccdaae7da0541e38d8e","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"016930dcf31640e5b23eacce30248809996dcdb5","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9e995b7ab3838ff50342d3a0a1bd79594112987","tid":1143034,"uid":181083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:39:30.000Z","msg":"依家幾多個人？"},{"pid":"141f2ca582874a4211f2dccb1fb354f77911c34b","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e995b7ab3838ff50342d3a0a1bd79594112987","tid":1143034,"uid":181083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:39:30.000Z","msg":"依家幾多個人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:56:44.000Z","msg":"16個咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20713c7e57f06643962b07d7ef5d27e83720ef71","tid":1143034,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci